FBIS4-39696 "drsov112_a_94019" FBIS-SOV-94-112 Daily Report 9 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Yeltsin Receives Italian Prime Minister's Envoy Yeltsin Receives Italian Prime Minister's Envoy LD0906151794 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1357 GMT 9 Jun 94 LD0906151794 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Text] Moscow June 9 TASS -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin received on Thursday Italian prime minister's envoy Pietro Calamia to discuss preparations for the G-7 summit in Naples and Russia's role in the activity of the G-7, the Russian presidential press service reported on Thursday.
